events.title: Once upon a time in the West
events.description: A mysterious stranger with a harmonica joins forces with a notorious desperado to protect a beautiful widow from a ruthless assassin working for the railroad.

events.title: Batman and Robin
events.description: Batman and Robin must stop Mr. Freeze and Poison Ivy from freezing Gotham City and enslaving its citizens.

events.title: Willy Wonka and the Chocolate Factory
events.description: A poor boy wins a golden ticket to visit Willy Wonka's mysterious chocolate factory.
